## Part 2


::: {.cell hash='2020-10_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_01071ea99748ece604f264b948ccbcb2'}

```{.r .cell-code}
df$paths <- 0
df$paths[1] <- 1
for(i in 2:nrow(df))
  for(x in 1:3)
    if((df$jolts[i] - x) %in% df$jolts)
      df$paths[i] <- df$paths[i] + df$paths[match(df$jolts[i] - x, df$jolts)]
format(df$paths[nrow(df) - 1], scientific=FALSE)
```

